description: Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) Maintenance and Support
full_summary:
# BPM020322 Eaton UPS Maintenance and Support

## Solicitation Overview

This is a re-solicitation of the original request for proposal (RFP) BPM020322 to allow vendors to correct pricing due to updated coverage. Shared Services Canada (SSC) has a requirement for the provision of Eaton Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) maintenance and support services.

### Key Details

* **Trade Agreement(s)**: This solicitation is available under the following trade agreements: WTO-AGP, CCFTA, CColFTA, CKFTA, CETA, ALEH, ALEPA, ALECUI, ACC Canada-UK, PTPGP, and ALEC
* **Closing Date**: February 29, 2024, at 2:00 PM Eastern Standard Time (EST)
* **Bidder Inquiries**: Suppliers may inquire or submit emails to `tenders-offres@ssc-spc.gc.ca`

### Overview

SSC is seeking a service provider to provide Eaton UPS maintenance and support services. This solicitation includes the following requirements:

* Security requirement: This solicitation contains a containment/processing-security requirement
* Maintenance support services for Eaton UPS systems

### Requirements

* **Security requirement**: This solicitation contains a containment/processing-security requirement
* **Trade Agreements**: World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO-AGP), Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement (CColFTA), Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA), Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA), Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement (ALEH), Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement (ALEPA), Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (ALECUI), Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (ACC), Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (PTPGP), and Canadian Free Trade Agreement (ALEC)
* **Closing Date**: February 29, 2024, at 2:00 PM EST

### Additional Information

* **Bidder Inquiries**: Suppliers may inquire or submit emails to `tenders-offres@ssc-spc.gc.ca`
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open Bidding
* **Notice Number**: SSC-24-00025694
* **Procurement ID**: BPM020322/25694

### Attachment

The following attachments are available for this solicitation:

* [Link to P2P Portal](https://sscp2pspc.ssc-spc
